		<blockquote class="quoteContainer"><div class="quote">I am looking at building a new nas based around freenas for a new media server, I am looking at building it with 8 internal 3tb hard drives and possible 4 external usb 3.0 3 tb hard drives in a potential raid 5 configuration.<br />
